"em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n"
"                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Validate&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;the "
"receipt&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n"
"                        &lt;/ul&gt;\n"
"                &lt;/div&gt;\n"
"                &lt;/div&gt;\n"
"                &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n"
"                &lt;h3&gt;🧮&lt;span style=\"width: 17px;\" class=\"oe-"
"tabs\"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;​Seasonal physical&amp;nbsp;inventory&amp;nbsp;"
"count&lt;/h3&gt;\n"
"                &lt;p&gt;\n"
"                In many countries, ensuring inventory accuracy is a legal "
"requirement. Use the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;font style=\"color: rgb(113, "
"75, 103);\"&gt;Physical Inventory&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;​ feature in the "
